Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fs50\pos(1055,1010)}Necro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}苦しみだけ置いていくはず
